  "text": "IMT study and endothelial adhesion molecules in the foreign general population reported that the risk of myocardial infarction increased in IMT value >0.82 mm (0.82-1.2 mm). 14 Study of atherosclerosis risk in the community (ARIC) reported that IMT value increases 0.01 mm/year in the hypertension population. [CITATION_1] There are not study that evaluated IMT progression associated with hsCRP, eNOS gene polymorphism, and IL −174 G/C gene polymorphism in the Indonesian population.",
